title: Testament of Youth. Official Movie Trailer #1 [HD] (2015)
description:
In theaters: June 5th, 2015

Description:

Testament of Youth is a powerful story of love, war and remembrance, based on the First World War memoir by Vera Brittain which has become the classic testimony of that war from a woman's point of view. A searing journey from youthful hopes and dreams to the edge of despair and back again, it's a film about young love, the futility of war and how to make sense of the darkest times.

Director: James Kent

Writers: Screenplay by Juliette Towhidi, Based on Vera Brittain's memoir

Actors: Alicia Vikander, Kit Harington, Taron Egerton, Emily Watson, Hayley Atwell, Colin Morgan, Joanna Scanlan, Dominic West, Miranda Richardson

Genre: Drama

Run Time: 2 hours 9 minutes
